cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is about natural language processing and specifically focuses on implicit discourse relation recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper proposes a deep learning model with different levels of text representation, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper uses neural networks to improve the performance of the model, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves optimization techniques to improve the model's performance, which is related to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves text classification, which is related to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
